St. Louis, Jacksonville & Chicago Railroad Company v. David Winter.Appeal from the Circuit Court of Morgan county; the Hon. D. M. Woodson, Judge, presiding.

This case presents the same questions decided in the preceding case.

Messrs. Ketcham & Atkins, for the appellant.Messrs. Morrison & Epler, for the appellee. Mr. Justice Walker:

This case is, in all material respects, identical with the preceding case, and the judgment is affirmed.

Judgment affirmed.
